; Same mutating plugin invoked twice in a single pipeline. Each pass
; doubles amounts, so postings end up at 4x the source value. Verifies
; that chained plugin runs compose correctly (and that the runner
; performs a single Data <-> Lua roundtrip across the whole chain).
plugin "plugin_pipeline_double"
plugin "plugin_pipeline_double"

2024-01-01 open Assets:Cash USD
2024-01-01 open Expenses:Food

2024-01-02 * "groceries"
  Assets:Cash    -10.00 USD
  Expenses:Food
